We on Team 93 had a semi-similar issue. Ours came from the WCP Break-out board though. We have pins that go on every connector on the WCP Break-out board for Kraken X60’s and when we took a HARD side impact during a match we had the entire Powerpole connection come off of the breakout board. The housing was still intact but it came off of the board entirely. Not a completely similar issue since we didn’t have it happen to the Kraken itself since it was just the break-out board. That bolt sheering though is CRAZY!
